<Window x:Class="photomixerGUI.ProjectInfo"
        xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
        xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
        xmlns:local="clr-namespace:photomixerGUI"
        mc:Ignorable="d"
        Title="ProjectInfo" Height="500" Width="800">

    <Grid Background="Black">

        <Label Content="Welcome!" FontSize="20" Foreground="White" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Margin="0,10,0,383"/>

        <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Center" FontSize="15" Foreground="White" Margin="0,70,0,70" Width="644">  
            Hi:) We are Ines and Shelly, and we did this project on behalf of the "Magshimim" program.<LineBreak />
            <LineBreak />
            Our project let you upload images - images that you found online or toke yourself,<LineBreak />
             and then our program will recognize the object in the image.<LineBreak />
            After that, you can put the image on a background to your choice, and save it.<LineBreak />
            <LineBreak />
            For the object detection to work, your image must meet the following criteria: <LineBreak />
            1. Object/background are not in black and white colors<LineBreak />
            2. Object and background are not in similar colors<LineBreak />
            3. The object covers most of the image<LineBreak />
            <LineBreak />
            Sign up to get complete security - encryption of your images!<LineBreak />
            <LineBreak />
            Hope you'll enjoy:)<LineBreak />
        </TextBlock>

    </Grid>
</Window>
